# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Final10 root .gitignore
#
# Intentionally aggressive about env files and build artifacts so secrets
# cannot silently land in the repo. If you need a committed example file,
# use `.env.example` (checked in) — never `.env*`.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Dependencies
node_modules/
**/node_modules/

# Environment & secrets — NEVER commit any of these
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.mobileprovision
GoogleService-Info.plist
google-services.json

# Build artifacts
build/
dist/
.next/
.out/
coverage/
.nyc_output/

# Logs
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# Runtime / temp
pids
*.pid
*.seed
*.pid.lock
*.tmp
*.temp

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Local tooling
.cursor/
.claude/
